posts.title: President Trump should continue to give RFK air time
posts.content:
RFK has a much bigger following then many people realize. Trump should let him talk about his policies that Trump wants him to put in action. Trump knows he can not let him go into environmental green new deal shit, because his base will not go for that. But stuff like the FDA where they are poisoning us with our food is something that needs to be brought to EVERYONES attention.

While RFK has some very different views then most of us, primarily on the environment and climate change, he has a lot of aligning views.

RFK is very anti big pharma. He is has literally written books calling them out as well as Fauci.

RFK endorsing Trump isn't enough to sway all his followers. But if Trump gives him a legitimate platform, which the DNC refused to do, it can help capture the rest of the votes.

Personal friend of mine is a big RFK supporter and does not support Trump. Blasphemous, I know, but we respect each others views and have actual intellectual debates to understand each others view points. We have been talking and I can already see his mind changing about voting for Trump, especially by him letting RFK speak.
